headline: This Pest Control Name Outperforms As It Sits In A Buy Zone
summary: Leading pest control provider Rollins is outperforming in a tough market.  Rollins' brands include Orkin, Clark Control and Critter Control.  Its provides termite and insect control, and rodent and wildlife removal.
